 />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n張工作不夠好"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T13:05:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T13:25:51.000Z","msg":"其實實際上要做咩工作"},{"pid":"ceb5840f33fe60e63ee554374363c5e385f130a2","tid":711251,"uid":33668,"like":24,"dislike":3,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T01:42:39.000Z","msg":"9估<br />\n<br />\n我估之前一哥同無記鬧翻係因為數口搞唔清<br />\n<br />\n又咁啱比佢周到呢個犯眾爭 (包括無記) 的經理食夾棍 一哥先督個經理出嚟硬食咗佢<br />\n<br />\n然後同無記重收舊口<br />\n<br />\n講真平時食夾棍常有駕啦 一般都私了 搞到上法庭做場大龍鳳真係少而有知 因為你爆一單嘢出嚟<br />\n<br />\n其他客仔知道咗可能都會打蛇隨棍上<br />\n<br />\n佢班養唔熟 簽翻嚟果堆藝人又會成機屈水 未必琴得住把火"},{"pid":"c31894d3c427a595131488607c9736e1be200cec","tid":711251,"uid":55913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T01:57:06.000Z","msg":"蕭生識玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5bb23153d8ad42c1438957876faf58678a34f4d","tid":711251,"uid":67500,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T01:58:44.000Z","msg":"TB...D手法咁低裝...係人都捉到你啦"},{"pid":"e06d884af85919feb253dbad8033167ed601540d","tid":711251,"uid":23707,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"60bec3222df99ebca2a43d0b374178d30e91d41f","tid":711251,"uid":26451,"like":80,"dislike":1,"score":79,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T12:18:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T01:59:06.000Z","msg":"大把師奶同妹妹仔出哂水啦"},{"pid":"2f98e967e4699bc6ef3b907cbf61ade56f7d39c7","tid":711251,"uid":113626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T02:01:20.000Z","msg":"呢d咪就係吸血鬼<br />\n想不勞而獲獲取利益"},{"pid":"bddf5749cd3f09faaa1e9ae742ee97a5c3ae07fc","tid":711251,"uid":28435,"like":157,"dislike":0,"score":157,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T03:04:48.000Z","msg":"chilam控制到自己唔會表現多過388萬 <img src=\"/assets